sort on doc-nbr 

set subfile name docpaycode4 keep at doc-nbr
report &
doc-name  &
doc-inits  &
doc-full-part-ind  &
doc-nbr   &
doc-dept  &
doc-clinic-nbr &
doc-pay-code &
